# Propagated Session LLM Selection to Autonomous Loops & Skills

We successfully completed the implementation to propagate the active chat session's configured LLM provider and model (`openai / gpt-5-mini`) to the PRISM Autonomous Loop and Skills Engine.

## Changes Made

### 1. Skills Engine
- **File modified:** [skills-engine.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/skills/skills-engine.ts)
- Retrieved the parent chat session details using `this.chatStore` and `session.parentChatSession`.
- Constructed a selection object containing the session's active `llmProviderId` and `llmModel`.
- Passed the selection as the second parameter to `this.providerManager.generate(..., selection)`.

### 2. Autonomous Agent Loop
- **File modified:** [autonomous-agent-loop.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/runtime/autonomous-agent-loop.ts)
